divs: sighting detailsi was on my way to work from south austin when i noticed a brightly colored object in the sky. i believed it was a plane at first. when i stopped at a stop sign, i noticed the object moved very quickly and seemed to hover at times. the object also pulsated between blue and a very bright neon green. at this point i started recording it with my phone. the object seemed to speed up and slow down a few times while pulsating the different colors. it then very quickly moved behind the hills where i could no longer see it. the video is not very high quality, due to it being recorded on my phone.
